name: SwiftUI Inspector
description:
SwiftUI inspector is here. Enhance your development workflow by copying and pasting element styles from your Figma files into your Xcode project.


Now with support for Auto Layout frames and manual stacking.


Supported:

- Colors

- Color Styles

- Text Labels

- Basic Shapes

- Frames

- Auto Layout

- Drop Shadows

- Gradients

- Components

- Layer opacity

- Layer blending modes


Looking forward to your feedback.
